<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 description">
        WingtipTickets is a sample application that provides a ticketing solution to Tenants (Artists) using Microsoft’s rich cloud platform: Microsoft Azure. The purpose of WingtipTickets is to demonstrate the power of Microsoft Azure, from the perspective of an ISV, and isn’t intended to be a complete ticketing solution.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row spacer-25">
</div>

<!-- -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -->
<!-- HEADER -->
